ion, we confirm findings from previous\nanalytic modeling that the spectral energy distribution varies significantly\nwith orbital orientation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 May 2014 11:11:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
